%h1{:style => "text-align:left;"} App User Referrals
%p{:style => "text-align:left;padding-bottom:10px;"} You know the feeling when you read something and you think of a friend. Maybe it’s a common joke you have or maybe you think your friend could be interested in what you are reading. Content sharing makes it simple and easy for your users to share pieces of content in your app with their friends and contacts.
